DATA DISCLAIMER:

This database compiles publicly available information from authoritative sources
including Truth Initiative, Campaign for Tobacco-Free Kids, Tax Foundation, CDC,
FDA, and state legislative sources. While we strive for accuracy, this database
is provided for research and informational purposes only. Users should consult
primary sources and official state resources for legal and regulatory decisions.

The data is current as of December 2024/January 2025 and is subject to change
as states update their policies.
